Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.44,0:00:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.32,0:00:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.13,0:00:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.71,0:00:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.82,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.33,0:01:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.96,0:01:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.87,0:01:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.42,0:01:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無名的人們啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集合維持獨立的個體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷改革世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.70,0:01:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為系統的壽命已經瀕臨終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民的自殺炸彈恐怖行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對政治的不信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來自各國的摩擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包圍這個國家的情勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化為集合體的個人將拯救之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.18,0:02:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺醒吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無名的人們啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後成為系統的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.59,0:02:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃13  臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.22,0:02:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—喂!聲音有放進7點新聞嗎?\N—將難民的愚行視為宣戰佈告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—有放進去?\N—引導他們邁向解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—好 我們這邊來拍影像\N—我們堅決完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—小杉 你看那個\N—身為先驅應有的奉獻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後今天將執行最後的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼承我們的意志！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—等一下\N—毋需多言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們用刀砍下了彼此的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個接一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.92,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相砍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是難以置信的景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現在屋頂的男子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—停\N—似乎拿刀互砍而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.76,0:02:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是昨天下午七點突然出現在國營電視台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心想他們總算現身了\N怎麼突然鬧自殺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.51,0:03:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓人想起從合田的虛擬人格身上做人物側寫所得的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創造引發Stand Alone Complex現象的媒介者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.35,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「英雄因其死亡而誕生」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.82,0:03:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與Patrick Sylvestre評論古巴革命的話一致的行動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.83,0:03:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還很細心地捏造「個別的11人」這個幻象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧妙掩飾這是病毒引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了我去見的那個記者之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.41,0:03:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全國應該還有很多人莫名其妙企圖自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說我也很危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以確定程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.39,0:03:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就設定好讓感染病毒的人最後去自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民已經用自爆的手段展開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.53,0:04:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不知道這次自殺報導會出現多少模仿者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這次應該會讓大多數不自覺的一般市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.24,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深深瞭解到這個國家存在難民問題這個火藥庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不讓感染病毒的病患再度出現癥狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們需要疫苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.18,0:04:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田的計劃恐怕也不過是第一階段終了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然很擔心難民和模仿者的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.33,0:04:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過人數居於劣勢的9課已經無法應付了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我們要集中以內廳為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了這個目的還是有必要抓住這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這傢伙到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼就他一個沒有自殺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要正確找出理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不解析他本人的電子腦是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們鑒識人員之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.75,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將這種感染同一病毒卻做出完全不同行動的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稱為「突發性異變體」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 從這個異變體的影像上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠看出什麼新的資訊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.57,0:05:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在襲擊首相時的影像中我們也注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙說話時不動嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.84,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一直以為在這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.08,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該是為了提升義體表現故意切斷神經網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.85,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 這次也看到同樣行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此似乎可以得出不同的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—等一下\N—毋需多言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕這傢伙幾乎沒有使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.47,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形成表情肌肉神經網絡的微機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示他不動嘴巴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 並非不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是幾乎不讓嘴巴動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這能成為追蹤那傢伙的線索嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來請看這傢伙的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有一張很帥的臉 對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事無關緊要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真是急性子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.89,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排除表情肌肉的使用\N為什麼還能有這麼像人類的臉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請技術高明的造顏作家做的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.81,0:06:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙的臉多半是超一流造顏作家的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作者並非身邊大企業環繞的藝術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那種技術的作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在國內只有兩名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到造顏作家這麼珍貴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.47,0:06:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本就有人說日本人雖然手巧卻不擅長寫實的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算會做既有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.21,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 擁有感性能創造出獨一無二臉龐的藝術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.58,0:06:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.84,0:06:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是9課的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.02,0:07:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 好像是殺人案件的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 剛到就碰到怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查對像有可能被滅口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被搶先一步嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 縣警因為殺人案件封鎖了工作室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我派帕茲與齋藤過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓現場被縣警弄亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是9課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以請你們所有人離開這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.92,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9課為什麼要出面干涉普通的殺人案?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被害人是造顏作家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.86,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實際上他是我們某追查中案件的重要關係人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 這件案子馬上就會解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓到犯人之後會給你們情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以請乖乖回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說馬上就會解決是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.04,0:08:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使不是鑒識人員也馬上看得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有可能採到指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.45,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且嫌犯跟被害人認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到犯案之前還在一起喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.95,0:08:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.19,0:08:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏的監視攝影機也清晰地拍下犯人的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.79,0:08:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒必要再進一步說明了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那給我們看看那個影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.67,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.83,0:08:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也可以強制剝奪你的指揮權喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會屈服在這種壓力下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不太平靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那張臉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.47,0:09:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實毫無疑問是帕茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證物上的指紋怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說是一致的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酒杯上的唇紋也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.15,0:09:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,費盡功夫才阻止那批叫囂著要逮捕帕茲的縣警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縣警那些人大概也能理解到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個影像無法當作決定性證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 連指紋和唇紋都一致事情可就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是這兩個證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不也都能偽造嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.03,0:09:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連記錄在義體上的DNA資料都偷的到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設犯人是那個義體混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能發生這種事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那恐怕很難想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許只是恰巧跟某個別的案件撞在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕茲 有沒有想到什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川與波瑪從回收的資料上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清查有沒有那個義體男子的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特、齋藤、托古薩跟縣警合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追查造顏作家的命案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕茲在嫌疑未洗清之前要注意自己的言行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到跟案件有關的情報全部都要向我報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有什麼理由才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有想到什麼事情吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不方便跟少校說 找我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想起什麼事情的話就說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成對的Death Mask\N（從死者臉上拓下的面模）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆娘的新興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我跟他一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有何貴幹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然想跟蹤你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過似乎馬上就會被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我並不認為你是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個城市當中\N連臉都義體化的傢伙並不稀奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那不只是同一張臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就跟你一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.78,0:11:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從那段影像上面感覺到某種對你的執著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人絕對跟你有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.35,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以讓我跟蹤你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚就是來打聲招呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.80,0:11:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然會帶著男性同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部分都是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.07,0:11:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者永遠是不同的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不認識的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,興趣變了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說那個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.32,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近認識了一位很棒的造顏作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造顏作家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.36,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然請他替我做了新的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 在試戴他做的臉時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我發現一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是靈魂有沒有可能不在腦殼裏面 而是在皮膚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是寄宿在臉上所刻畫的皺紋當中呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.61,0:12:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那位造顏作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.15,0:12:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直替在戰場上負傷的士兵做新的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會發現臉上傷痕的深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那位士兵心中傷痕的深度是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 原來是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就是這傢伙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他名叫久世英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身都義體化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從記錄上的規格來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是PKF型號的義體不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臉的訂單也如同鑒識官推理的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎沒有安裝神經網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.49,0:13:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是純粹靠造顏作家的技術\N表現出表情和皺褶的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是獨一無二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,材料是安裝有自我再生程序的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.83,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,納米碳分子以及人工生化皮膚的混合物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不知道有沒有直接關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過被殺害的造顏作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.51,0:14:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長年自願只替退伍軍人做臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙多半是聽到這個傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才來找他做自己的臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世英雄嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然當時的記錄已經銷毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有直接去調查他的行蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.06,0:14:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好飛去半島的準備工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這對老年人的身體不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在那邊你最吃得開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他跟這次的造顏作家命案沒有關聯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 犯人跟帕茲有某種關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定出乎意料地跟女人有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 事情不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縣警的刑事被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.69,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且被殺之前還跟帕茲見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕茲也在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.43,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很明顯這傢伙想要陷害帕茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從掉在地上的彈殼來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用的是SEBURO M5的專用彈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得太露骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.21,0:15:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕茲 事到如今\N還是沒想到什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如說實在太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被殺害的造顏作家的顧客資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從比較新的開始讓我看幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定會聯想到什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 這個事件現在起請讓我一個人追查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果造成什麼困擾的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以馬上把我幹掉沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.68,0:15:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這恐怕是非常私人的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 隨你高興怎麼做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是不是有什麼誤會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們想說他是嫌疑犯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,間接證據是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 他是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之要先查查看才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有這個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能性的話 我們早就動手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.92,0:16:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.49,0:16:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在你的外部記憶裏面輸入我現在要去的地方的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你去那裏看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然把我的事都忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過5年前 我們還住在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.31,0:18:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從什麼時候開始佔據了那個女人的義體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是3個月前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏偶然看到你的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完全沒發現 對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女人的腦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.49,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該在夢之島吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的指紋也是在那裏拿到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼想變成我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全無法理解你在我面前消失的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並沒有別的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.78,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你說不要問你的事 我就照辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.92,0:19:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你還是消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你第一次見到我的時候說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「我不跟同一個女人睡第二次」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始我還想這算什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次的時候我已經無法自拔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.27,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一點你應該也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好殘忍的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我瘋狂地恨著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.48,0:19:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明如此 我還是不斷思考你消失的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才去做臉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.89,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.96,0:20:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我愛的有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看的簡直就是兩個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.54,0:20:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不讓我看到那個世界於是你選擇消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要自視過高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你就是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是已經不重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經在身體裏面放進了你的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.73,0:20:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以已經不需要真正的你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果對我還有愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.58,0:21:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就請你死在這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被你所殺 正合我願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.10,0:21:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.14,0:21:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞定了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳細情況就像剛剛報告的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有帕茲風格的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.69,0:22:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.23,0:22:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.63,0:22:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該更早發現才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.57,0:22:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要殺他的女性說不定非常多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.51,0:22:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我沒有確認過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.78,0:22:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 當初去招攬他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.41,0:22:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也跟我說過「我不跟同一個女人睡第二次」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.79,0:22:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是敗給他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.92,0:22:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.96,0:22:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個帕茲應該是真的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.56,0:22:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.55,0:23:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.22,0:23:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.76,0:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.07,0:23:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.54,0:23:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.28,0:23:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我審視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.92,0:23:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.93,0:24:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軀殼裏的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.13,0:24:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.00,0:24:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我審視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.97,0:24:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.14,0:24:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.65,0:24:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.72,0:24:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這個軀殼裏

